msgid ""
"FreeRec 依赖 torchdata 0.7.0，因为更新版本不再支持 datapipe 功能。 ``freerec setup`` 会以 "
"``--no-deps`` 方式安装，避免覆盖你已有的 PyTorch。"
msgstr ""
"FreeRec depends on torchdata 0.7.0, as newer versions no longer support "
"the datapipe functionality. ``freerec setup`` installs it with "
"``--no-deps`` to avoid overwriting your existing PyTorch installation."

